{
  "stem": "802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a dance teacher in our building, and she gave us lessons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if we paid her for doing that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, yeah, we did ballet, my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then many people moved into the building who shared apartments with their relatives, and some of these children initially were involved in this, too, in the dancing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In some way, we were better off than a great many people, largely because we had our apartment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But ultimately, we were-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we had to leave the apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know which order to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Let me go in some chronological order what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When the roundups became more frequent, it was more and more difficult to leave your house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Initially, the roundups were largely from the street, in the streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Later, in 1942, in July, 1942, the decree to murder all the Jews came, and so things changed very, very dramatically.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was in July, as I believe I said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And at that point, the Germans, the Ukrainians, the Lithuanians-- maybe even before, but I don't remember that as clearly as I remember this-- came into the homes of the people and just picked up the people and took them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if you tried to fight or to resist, you were shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had no weapons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many people don't understand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They say, why didn't you fight back?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could only fight back with our spirit, with our, you know, moral strength.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the only weapon we had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were-- as a matter of fact, there were-- I'm going to backtrack, if I may-- there were prayer houses and there were soup kitchens.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were many self-help organizations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were orphanages for the children.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
